[node name="CreditHeader" type="Label" parent="Credits"]
layout_mode = 0
offset_left = 0.5
offset_top = 32.0
offset_right = 539.0
offset_bottom = 76.0
text = "FrankenChess Credits"
label_settings = SubResource("LabelSettings_k3576")
horizontal_alignment = 1

[node name="Morgan" type="Label" parent="Credits"]
self_modulate = Color(1, 1, 1, 0)
layout_mode = 0
offset_left = 0.5
offset_top = 91.0
offset_right = 538.0
offset_bottom = 305.0
text = "Morgan is like the Master Chef of the project. 
She has the vision of what she wants the project to be. 
She doesn’t have time to get her hands dirty with coding or 
game design when she has a vision to bring to life. 
She worked on implementing the assembly menu 
where pieces are built. 
She is also the proud owner of Cinder the cat.
"
label_settings = SubResource("LabelSettings_onyvc")
horizontal_alignment = 1

[node name="Byron" type="Label" parent="Credits"]
self_modulate = Color(1, 1, 1, 0)
layout_mode = 0
offset_top = 99.0
offset_right = 541.5
offset_bottom = 330.0
text = "Byron is like the Sous/Prep Chef of the project. 
He was down in the trenches working on the logistics of the project. 
Responsible for making the chess engine 
and main menu from scratch. 
He really is the most humble guy out there. 
When asked about his contributions to the project he said 
“I really am the backbone of the project.” 
He’s just so humble.
"
label_settings = SubResource("LabelSettings_6afij")
horizontal_alignment = 1

[node name="Smedley" type="Label" parent="Credits"]
self_modulate = Color(1, 1, 1, 0)
layout_mode = 0
offset_top = 76.0
offset_right = 538.5
offset_bottom = 437.0
text = "Smedley is like the janitor of the kitchen 
that ended up as a chef by accident. 
He doesn’t know what he’s doing, how he ended up in the class, 
or what Godot is, but his contributions are undeniable. 
He made the music and sound effects 
to really bring the game together. 
He also crafted the game over menu just for fun. 
When asked what his favorite cheese is he said: 
“All cheeses, except foot cheese. Feta up with everyone’s business.” 
As someone who says puns and unfunny jokes constantly, 
he is easily the most hated member of the team.
"
label_settings = SubResource("LabelSettings_tclov")
horizontal_alignment = 1

[node name="Joey" type="Label" parent="Credits"]
self_modulate = Color(1, 1, 1, 0)
layout_mode = 0
offset_left = 0.5
offset_top = 89.0
offset_right = 538.5
offset_bottom = 302.0
text = "Joey - “Whatever you think.”
Joey is our resident narcissist and sarcastic comic relief. 
He is not in any way helpful to the project in any way, shape, or form. 
If you say anything positive in the slightest, 
he will be sure to swat it down. 
At least he’s consistent. 
Get to know Joey, he will change your life."
label_settings = SubResource("LabelSettings_wxecf")
horizontal_alignment = 1

[node name="Jonathan" type="Label" parent="Credits"]
self_modulate = Color(1, 1, 1, 0)
layout_mode = 0
offset_top = 150.0
offset_right = 538.5
offset_bottom = 319.0
text = "Jonathan never really showed up to class, 
but he was responsible for the 3D models of all the pieces. 
I don’t know much about him, but he seems alright. 
The pieces are pretty dope.
"
label_settings = SubResource("LabelSettings_15tvp")
horizontal_alignment = 1

[node name="Corben" type="Label" parent="Credits"]
self_modulate = Color(1, 1, 1, 0)
layout_mode = 0
offset_top = 150.0
offset_right = 538.5
offset_bottom = 319.0
text = "Corben was there I think?"
label_settings = SubResource("LabelSettings_wd4nr")
horizontal_alignment = 1

[node name="Cinder" type="Label" parent="Credits"]
self_modulate = Color(1, 1, 1, 0)
layout_mode = 0
offset_top = 68.0
offset_right = 538.5
offset_bottom = 351.0
text = "Cinder! I can’t say enough about Cinder. 
Cinder was the true driving force of our team. 
If there is anything that the team was stuck on, 
she would immediately walk over and purr. 
This immediately brought wisdom, courage, and joy to everyone. 
She is a ball of sunshine that truly made the team better. 
Every single wall the team ran into was solved by Cinder. 
Cinder truly was the Queen to our King, 
while our team is a bunch of narrow-minded pawns. 
God bless Cinder. O7
"
label_settings = SubResource("LabelSettings_xjjoo")
horizontal_alignment = 1

